==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Laying
<hw>Lay"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of one who, or that which, lays.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act or period of laying eggs; the eggs laid for
one incubation; a clutch.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>The first coat on laths of plasterer's two-coat
work.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Layland</ent>⟦br⟧
